OL,3,CFundraiser launched for mother-of-
OL,4,Cthree found dead in Hawick
OL,6,FPolice were called to the property on
OL,7,FMcLagan Drive at around 7.20am on
OL,8,FThursday 25 June.
OL,10,FA 39-year-old man was arrested and
OL,11,Fcharged in connection with Stacey's
OL,12,Fdeath. He appeared at Selkirk Sheriff
OL,13,FCourt on Friday 26 June.
OL,15,FIn an earlier statement, Police
OL,16,FScotland said: "Around 7.20am on
OL,17,FThursday, 25 June, 2026, we were
OL,18,Fcalled to the death of a 35-year-old
OL,19,Fwoman at a property on McLagan Drive
OL,20,Fin Hawick. Next of kin is aware."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
